longBusinessSummary: China Dili Group, an investment holding company, engages in the operating, leasing, and managing agriculture wholesale markets in the People's Republic of China. It operates 10 wholesale markets in Harbin, Qiqihar, Mudanjiang, Shenyang, Shouguang, Guiyang, and Hangzhou. The company was formerly known as Renhe Commercial Holdings Company Limited and changed its name to China Dili Group in June 2019. China Dili Group was founded in 2002 and is based in Wanchai, Hong Kong.
